public class LinearUnit
extends FactorBasedUnit
implements Unit

A LinearUnit is is a factor based unit that utilizes a factor to convert to and from meters. The following is a partial table:

  • [$Linear Units$, LinearUnit]
  • //NAME, DESC, LONG DESC, SUFFIX, FACTOR, NUMBER OF PLACES AFTER DECIMAL- default
  • FEET, "Int. Feet", "International Feet", "ft", 3.280839895, 3
  • METER, "METER", "METER", "m", 1.0, 3
  • MM, "Millimeter", "", "mm", 1000, 3
  • CM, "Centimeter", "", "cm", 100, 3
  • DM, "Decimeter", "", "dc", 10, 3
  • KM, "Kilometer", "", "km", 0.001, 3
